  <slide>
    <title>H2L: Side Panel Features</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Uses <a href="https://opena11y.github.io/evaluation-library/">OpenA11y Evaluation Library</a></li>
        <li>Computes <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/accname-1.2/">accessible names using W3C algorithm</a></li>
        <li>Emulates screen reader filtering of headings and landmarks:
          <ul>
            <li>Removes small and off-screen headings</li>
            <li>Landmarks without accessible names</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>

  <slide>
    <title>H2L: Options</title>
    <contents>

      <figure class="image">
         <img src="./images/h2l-options.png"
              alt=""/>
              <figcaption>Screen shot of Headings, Landmarks and Links Options Page</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Options</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Highlight styling</li>
        <li>Landmarks without names (i.e. screen readers ignore them)</li>
        <li>Link Filters:
          <ul>
            <li>Internal links</li>
            <li>Same sub-domain links</li>
            <li>Same domain links</li>
            <li>External links</li>
            <li>Non-HTML links (e.g. PDF, Excel, Docs)</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

    </contents>
  </slide>


